description: The walk will take in East India Dock Basin, Bow Creek and Trinity Buoy Wharf looking at the history of the area. Wildlife is also a key subject on East India Dock Basin and birdwatchers can bring binoculars.

events.name: East India Dock Basin Explorer
events.notes: Strong walking shoes are recommended but the route on this one is good and mostly surfaced paths. Bring some water and a snack and weather proof cloths if the weather looks like it might be wet.

facilities: Family activities during open house festival

factsheet.heading: History and Wildlife
paragraphs: This walk will highlight the history of the site and surrounding areas which date back to the early 1800's. Now wildlife call these places home so make sure you bring your binoculars
